Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:07.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（此处片头风格模仿自「Studio Ghibli」（吉卜力工作室）的龙猫标志）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  Cherry  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好！…真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家来做客  你要做个乖孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.20,0:01:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中女生
